---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="space-y-12">
    <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-900/80 p-10 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-950/30 backdrop-blur-xl">
      <span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-sky-500/15 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-sky-300">Data-AI-Resilience Lab</span>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">Welcome to the Data-Driven Hazard Mitigation and Advanced Infrastructure Resilience Lab.</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">The principal investigator is Dr. Peng-Yu Chen. The lab focuses on implementing data-driven artificial intelligence approaches to enhance infrastructure resilience under natural hazards.</p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-950/90 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">以 GNN、Bi-LSTM 和 Diffusion 模型驅動工程研究，提升 RC 結構於地震與極端災害下的韌性。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-950/90 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">核心領域</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">從結構健康監測到風險評估，我們專注於自然危害下的資料驅動結構工程與災害緩解。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-950/90 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">研究重點</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">結合機器學習與物理資訊方法，建立可解釋、可推廣的韌性分析與風險決策工具。</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_320px]">
      <div class="space-y-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-900/80 p-10 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-950/30 backdrop-blur-xl">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-400">About the Lab</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">融合 AI 與結構工程的跨領域研究平台</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-8">Data-AI-Resilience Lab is dedicated to advancing infrastructure resilience through data-driven artificial intelligence. Our work spans structural engineering, seismic risk assessment, and advanced simulation methods with a special emphasis on reinforced concrete systems.</p>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-950/90 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Principal Investigator</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">Dr. Peng-Yu Chen, Associate Professor at National Central University and PhD from UCLA.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-950/90 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Application Areas</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">Structural resilience, seismic performance evaluation, RC building risk assessment, and scientific computing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="space-y-6 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-950/80 p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-950/20 backdrop-blur-xl">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-400">Latest News</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">實驗室最新動態</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-300">
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-900/80 p-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-sky-300">2026/06</p>
            <p class="mt-2">啟動 HysRCDiffusion 框架測試，並準備整合 Google Scholar 論文自動更新機制。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-900/80 p-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-sky-300">2026/05</p>
            <p class="mt-2">擴展 RC 結構風險評估專案，聚焦於大型磚牆 (infill walls) 模擬挑戰。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/research" class="rounded-3xl border border-sky-500/20 bg-sky-500/10 px-4 py-4 text-sky-200 transition hover:bg-sky-500/20">探索研究計畫</a>
          <a href="/publications" class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-700/80 bg-slate-900/90 px-4 py-4 text-slate-200 transition hover:bg-slate-800/90">查看近期發表</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
